To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private DeMarkerIndicator _dem;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_dem = DEM(symbol, period, type);

// In OnData()
if (_dem.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "demarkerindicator", _dem.Current.Value);
}
